						<summary>

						<p>Stone set up near the entrance to the Rāmasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>Bikramahādityarāja (Vikramāditya).</p>						

						<p>Records a gift of land as <hi rend="italic">pannasa</hi> measured by the royal measure to Ālabōḷa Sabi Śarma at Koṇḍuru by Bikramahādityarāja of Solar race and Kāśyapa-<hi rend="italic">gōtra.</hi> In characters of the 7th-8th century A.D.</p>						

